query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `conversions` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `fromAsset` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `toAsset` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `fromAmount` decimal(20, 8) NOT NULL,
  `toAmount` decimal(20, 8) NOT NULL,
  `rate` decimal(20, 8) NOT NULL,
  `fee` decimal(20, 8) NOT NULL,
  `feePercentage` decimal(5, 2) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.5,
  `status` enum('pending', 'completed', 'failed') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'completed',
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `conversions_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
